</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\nClean&amp;Clean supplies everything needed for the required cleaning service free of charge. We’ll not try to charge you any additional fees for cleaning materials and equipment.\r\n\r\n<p class="number-list-heading"><strong><em>2) Do you charge extra on weekends and bank holidays? </em></strong></p>\r\n\r\nClean&amp;Clean would not charge you extra for bookings on weekends and bank holidays. We work 7 days a week including bank holidays and the price always remains the same.\r\n\r\n<p class="number-list-heading"><em><strong>3) </strong><strong>Do you charge VAT or any other additional fees? </strong></em></p>\r\n\r\nClean&amp;Clean would not charge you VAT. Thus, the price you are quoted is the price you would pay for the service. No additional fees or hidden costs.\r\n\r\n<p class="number-list-heading"><strong><em>4) Is oven cleaning included? </em></strong></p>\r\n\r\nClean&amp;Clean will clean your oven inside and out as part of our End of tenancy Cleaning Service. Further, we’ll clean all other cleaning appliances free of charge.\r\n\r\n<p class="number-list-heading"><strong><em>5) Do you clean windows? </em></strong></p>\r\n\r\nInternal window cleaning is included, but we can also clean your windows externally as long as our cleaners can reach them for an additional charge.\r\n\r\n<p class="number-list-heading"><strong>6) Do you take a deposit?  </strong></p>\r\n\r\nFor smaller jobs, you don’t have to pay anything upfront. For some larger properties, 10% deposit may be required to be paid on the day.\r\n\r\n<p class="number-list-heading"><strong><em>7) Are you insured? </em></strong></p>\r\n\r\nWe have full public liability insurance up to £1,000,000 and employers liability insurance specifically designed for a cleaning services company.\r\n\r\n<p class="number-list-heading"><em><strong>8)</strong></em> <strong><em>Do you defrost the freezer?</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\nThe freezer has to be defrosted by the client to ensure that our cleaners can clean the unit inside and out.\r\n\r\n<p class="number-list-heading"><strong><em>9) </em></strong><strong><em>Do you work outside London?</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\nWe provide services to all London postcodes and some areas within M25 only.\r\n\r\n<p class="number-list-heading"><em><strong>10)</strong></em> <strong><em>Do you clean walls?</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\nWe don’t clean walls as when treated the paint can be damaged. Further, it is not an end of tenancy cleaning requirement.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>Our team is ready to provide you with a bespoke end of tenancy cleaning service so why don’t you give us a call today. We are looking forward to hear from you.</em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</section>', 'End of tenancy cleaning', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'end-of-tenancy-cleaning', '', '', '2017-04-26 00:18:01', '2017-04-26 00:18:01', '', 0, 'http://cleanandclean.24s.us/?page_id=27', 0, 'page', '', 0),
