(48, 2, '2017-04-11 13:18:36', '2017-04-11 13:18:36', '<section class="after-cleaning col-sm-12">\r\n<img src="http://cleanandclean.24s.us/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/after-cleaning.jpg" alt=""class="alignleft" />\r\n\r\nHave you had builders working at your property? Have they left a mess behind them? Clean&amp;Clean can help you to clean your property leaving no dust behind. Our vast experience in conducting after builders cleaning can guarantee your full satisfaction. We won’t leave the premises until you are fully satisfied with our cleaning service.\r\n\r\nOur cleaning teams are fully equipped, insured, and vetted to ensure quality service and professionalism. We work 7 days a week including bank holidays at no additional charge. Our prices are fixed and unlike others we don’t do hidden charges. What you will be quoted is what you will be paying for the service.\r\n\r\nWe also have professional and up to date cleaning equipment that we successfully utilise in our cleanings. Let us help you get you property back into shape and dust free. Our cleaners undergo extensive in house training and all our personnel is working directly for the company.\r\n\r\n<strong>After Builders Cleaning benefits:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Removing of labels from bathrooms and kitchen appliances</li>\r\n 	<li>Dusting walls and ceilings</li>\r\n 	<li>Oven cleaning and all other kitchen appliances cleaned inside/out</li>\r\n 	<li>Vacuum and mop all floors throughout the property</li>\r\n 	<li>Cleaning materials and equipment included</li>\r\n 	<li>Satisfaction Guaranteed</li>\r\n 	<li>24/7 customer support</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="italic">In addition to your after builders cleaning you can book carpet or upholstery cleaning service. By booking two or more services together we can provide you with great savings. Call our friendly team today to find out more, or simply visit this <a href="/prices">page</a> for pricing.</p>\r\n</section>', 'After builders cleaning', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'after-builders-cleaning', '', '', '2017-04-24 12:03:22', '2017-04-24 12:03:22', '', 0, 'http://cleanandclean.24s.us/?page_id=48', 0, 'page', '', 0),
