(86, 2, '2017-04-24 12:50:39', '2017-04-24 12:50:39', '<section class="removals-services col-sm-12">\n<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/removals-services.jpg" alt=""  class="alignleft " />\n\nMoving house with all those possessions can seem impossible task. Some people try to move all their possessions by themselves. But why you should do it? Hiring professional removals services won’t cost the world and will save you a lot of time and headache. Not to mention the fact that you will have to pack everything, buying boxes and tapes. Be mindful that you have to know how to pack fragile items that can easily brake.\n\nLuckily, Clean&amp;Clean can provide you with specialised removals service that can be added to your end of tenancy cleaning service. We’ll perform everything on the same day and within few hours we’ll have you moved out successfully. Our movers are comprehensively trained in moving any object size and will carefully put it into boxes ready to be transported to your new place. You can depend on us to securely package your items.\n\nWe work 7 days a week including bank holidays, and you will not be charged extra. While our movers transport your precious items, have our end of tenancy cleaning teams to clean your property professionally ready to be handed over on the same day.\n\n<strong>Removals Services benefits:</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Domestic removals services</li>\n 	<li>Packaging and wrapping included</li>\n 	<li>Full insurance</li>\n 	<li>Fully trained and capable staff</li>\n 	<li>Customer Satisfaction Guaranteed</li>\n 	<li>7 days a week availability</li>\n</ul>\n<p class="italic">After removing all your possessions successfully you are most likely required to organise an end of tenancy or one off cleaning service. We offer great discounts by booking your removals services with one or more of our services together. Call our friendly team today to find out how much you can save or you can visit this <a href="/prices">page</a> for pricing and offers.</p>', 'Removals services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '54-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-04-24 12:50:39', '2017-04-24 12:50:39', '', 54, 'http://cleanandclean.24s.us/2017/04/12/54-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
