(94, 2, '2017-04-24 12:40:10', '2017-04-24 12:40:10', '<section class="move-cleaning col-sm-12">\n<img src="http://cleanandclean.24s.us/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/one-off-300x146.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="146" class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-212" />\n\nDo you have a party coming up? Or you simply want to impress your friends by sparkle cleaning your property. Whatever your needs, Clean&amp;Clean can help. We can provide you with a specialised one off cleaning service that’s tailored to suit all individual needs. Rest assured that our professional cleaning teams will get back your property into shape.\n\nUnlike our competitors our one off cleaning service is extensive involving cleaning your property from top to bottom. We will not cut corners, we’ll clean them. Our cleaning teams are fully insured, equipped and vetted for your piece of mind. We’ll supply all the cleaning materials needed for the job; hence you don’t have to provide anything. We work 7 days a week including bank holidays, and can respond to urgent enquiries often on the same day.\n\nSatisfaction is guaranteed. We won’t leave your premises until you are completely satisfied with our work. Booking our services will also save you time and money that can be wasted by hiring other unprofessional cleaning companies that provide poor service. This is not us. Our aim is to constantly improve on customer satisfaction and deliver high quality customer service that is competitive and affordable.\n\n<strong>One off cleaning benefits:</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Satisfaction Guaranteed</li>\n 	<li>24/7 Customer support</li>\n 	<li>Cleaning materials included</li>\n 	<li>Oven cleaning included</li>\n 	<li>Rapid response often on the same day</li>\n 	<li>Professional cleaning teams</li>\n 	<li>Fully insured cleaning company</li>\n 	<li>Fixed fees no hidden charges</li>\n</ul>\n<p class="italic">Do you need any other services along with your one off cleaning such as carpet cleaning or upholstery? If so, we can