(112, 2, '2017-04-12 13:02:33', '2017-04-12 13:02:33', '<h1>Move in/out cleaning</h1>\r\nClean&amp;Clean is London’s best-known cleaning company for providing specialist move out cleaning services. Moving out of a property is stressful enough, and to deal with all those cleaning chores would add more strain. Save yourself the trouble of cleaning and hire professionals to do it for you. We offer top rated cleaning services at the most competitive rates in London. Our cleaners are insured, trained, and vetted for additional piece of mind.\r\n\r\nWe use the latest equipment and technology in conducting move in/out cleaning services. Our experienced cleaners can advise you on the best cleaning methods for your property to ensure quality and efficiency. We’ll also provide you with all cleaning materials and equipment; hence you don’t have to supply anything for the cleaning. We work 7 days a week including bank holidays with no extra charges.\r\n\r\nOur move in/out cleaning is very comprehensive, and we’ll clean your property from top to bottom. Oven cleaning is included internally and externally as well as all other kitchen appliances. Windows will be cleaned internally and externally where accessible.\r\n\r\n<strong>Move in/out cleaning benefits:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Satisfaction Guaranteed</li>\r\n 	<li>Cleaning materials and equipment included</li>\r\n 	<li>Oven clean included</li>\r\n 	<li>24/7 Customer support</li>\r\n 	<li>Rapid response often on the same day</li>\r\n 	<li>Insured cleaning service</li>\r\n 	<li>Professionally in-house trained cleaning teams</li>\r\n 	<li>Comprehensive cleaning service (top to bottom)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe do offer great package deals when you incorporate two or more services together. Our offers constantly change, so why don’t you call our friendly team to find out how much you can save. Alternatively, you can visit this <a href="/prices" target="_self">page</a> for pricing and offers.', 'Move in/out cleaning', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '50-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-12 13:02:33', '2017-04-12 13:02:33', '', 50, 'http://cleanandclean.24s.us/2017/04/12/50-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(113, 2, '2017-04-12 13:02:47', '2017-04-12 13:02:47', '<h1>One off cleaning</h1>\r\nDo you have a party coming up? Or you simply want to impress your friends by sparkle cleaning your property. Whatever your needs, Clean&amp;Clean can help. We can provide you with a specialised one off cleaning service that’s tailored to suit all individual needs. Rest assured that our professional cleaning teams will get back your property into shape.\r\n\r\nUnlike our competitors our one off cleaning service is extensive involving cleaning your property from top to bottom. We will not cut corners, we’ll clean them. Our cleaning teams are fully insured, equipped and vetted for your piece of mind. We’ll supply all the cleaning materials needed for the job; hence you don’t have to provide anything. We work 7 days a week including bank holidays, and can respond to urgent enquiries often on the same day.\r\n\r\nSatisfaction is guaranteed. We won’t leave your premises until you are completely satisfied with our work. Booking our services will also save you time and money that can be wasted by hiring other unprofessional cleaning companies that provide poor service. This is not us. Our aim is to constantly improve on customer satisfaction and deliver high quality customer service that is competitive and affordable.\r\n\r\n<strong>One off cleaning benefits:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Satisfaction Guaranteed</li>\r\n 	<li>24/7 Customer support</li>\r\n 	<li>Cleaning materials included</li>\r\n 	<li>Oven cleaning included</li>\r\n 	<li>Rapid response often on the same day</li>\r\n 	<li>Professional cleaning teams</li>\r\n 	<li>Fully insured cleaning company</li>\r\n 	<li>Fixed fees no hidden charges</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDo you need any other services along with your one off cleaning such as carpet cleaning or upholstery? If so, we can give you great discounts on booking two or more services together. Simply, call our friendly team today to find out how much you can save. Alternatively, you can visit our prices <a href="/prices" target="_self">page</a> for more info.', 'One off cleaning', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '52-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-12 13:02:47', '2017-04-12 13:02:47', '', 52, 'http://cleanandclean.24s.us/2017/04/12/52-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(114, 2, '2017-04-12 13:03:34', '2017-04-12 13:03:34', '<h1>Removals services</h1>\r\nMoving house with all those possessions can seem impossible task. Some people try to move all their possessions by themselves. But why you should do it? Hiring professional removals services won’t cost the world and will save you a lot of time and headache. Not to mention the fact that you will have to pack everything, buying boxes and tapes. Be mindful that you have to know how to pack fragile items that can easily brake.\r\n\r\nLuckily, Clean&amp;Clean can provide you with specialised removals service that can be added to your end of tenancy cleaning service. We’ll perform everything on the same day and within few hours we’ll have you moved out successfully. Our movers are comprehensively trained in moving any object size and will carefully put it into boxes ready to be transported to your new place. You can depend on us to securely package your items.\r\n\r\nWe work 7 days a week including bank holidays, and you will not be charged extra. While our movers transport your precious items, have our end of tenancy cleaning teams to clean your property professionally ready to be handed over on the same day.\r\n\r\n<strong>Removals Services benefits:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Domestic removals services</li>\r\n 	<li>Packaging and wrapping included</li>\r\n 	<li>Full insurance</li>\r\n 	<li>Fully trained and capable staff</li>\r\n 	<li>Customer Satisfaction Guaranteed</li>\r\n 	<li>7 days a week availability</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAfter removing all your possessions successfully you are most likely required to organise an end of tenancy or one off cleaning service. We offer great discounts by booking your removals services with one or more of our services together. Call our friendly team today to find out how much you can save or you can visit this <a href="/prices">page</a> for pricing and offers.', 'Removals services', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '54-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-0