(259, 2, '2017-04-25 12:13:47', '2017-04-25 12:13:47', '<section class="tenansy-cleaning col=sm-12">\r\n<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/window-clean-stock-today-150514-tease_cb08b0d95b87a2f893666ba5b3433a28.today-inline-large-300x169.jpg" alt="" class="alignleft" />\r\n\r\nIs it time to move out? Wondering who to hire for your end of tenancy cleaning? Look nowhere else for the best end of tenancy cleaning company. We have been providing an end of tenancy cleaning in London for nearly a decade. Through our vast experience in conducting an end of tenancy cleaning services, we know the requirements of the leading estate agents in the capital and will deliver outstanding service every time.\r\n\r\nOur cleaning teams are fully equipped, trained, vetted, and insured to guarantee best cleaning experience possible. Unlike other cleaning companies who employ subcontractors to do their work, we provide in-house training and all our cleaners work directly for the company. This ensures quality, reliability, and efficiency.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Some of the benefits of our End of Tenancy Cleaning service:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Oven Clean included</li>\r\n 	<li>24/7 Customer support</li>\r\n 	<li>NO hidden charges</li>\r\n 	<li>NO VAT</li>\r\n 	<li>Fixed fees</li>\r\n 	<li>Cleaning materials and equipment supplied</li>\r\n 	<li>NO time limit</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur brand is associated with excellent customer support and outstanding cleaning services. Should you have any questions or concerns, our phone lines are open 24/7. You can book your end of tenancy cleaning service for the date and time that suits you. Our professional cleaning teams work 7 days a week including bank holidays. And what is even better is that we won’t charge you extra for bookings on weekends and bank holidays. It’s always a flat fixed fee. Unlike others, we don’t do hidden costs. What you will be quoted is what you will be paying. Don’t gamble with your money and hire professional today to free you of all cleaning chores.\r\n\r\n<strong>Please have a look at our End of Tenancy Cleaning checklist:</strong>\r\n<div class="row"><aside class="col-sm-6"><strong>Kitchen</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>De-scale sink and taps and polish surfaces</li>\r\n 	<li>Wipe clean inside all cupboards and drawers</li>\r\n 	<li>Wash and clean all work surfaces</li>\r\n 	<li>Floors to be cleaned, vacuumed, and mopped</li>\r\n 	<li>All kitchen appliances including oven to be cleaned inside/out</li>\r\n 	<li>Wipe clean light fittings</li>\r\n 	<li>Wipe clean skirting boards</li>\r\n 	<li>Bins to be cleaned inside/out</li>\r\n 	<li>Clean the extractor fan</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</aside><aside class="col-sm-12"><strong>Bathroom</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>De-scale shower area</li>\r\n 	<li>Wipe clean tiles and fittings</li>\r\n 	<li>Wipe clean windows and mirrors</li>\r\n 	<li>De-scale and disinfect toilet inside/out</li>\r\n 	<li>Wipe clean ventilation extractor if accessible</li>\r\n 	<li>Floors vacuumed, washed and mopped</li>\r\n 	<li>Wipe clean skirting boards</li>\r\n 	<li>Any cupboards or fixtures to be cleaned</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</aside>\r\n<div class="clearfix hiddex-xs"></div>\r\n<aside class="col-sm-12"><strong>Bedrooms</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>All Furniture to be wipe cleaned inside/out</li>\r\n 	<li>All doors and hinges to be cleaned</li>\r\n 	<li>Windows and mirrors to be wiped leaving no smears</li>\r\n 	<li>Light fittings to be wipe cleaned</li>\r\n 	<li>Vacuum under bed and furniture</li>\r\n 	<li>Cobwebs cleaned from ceilings</li>\r\n 	<li>Floors vacuumed, and mopped where applicable</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</aside><aside class="col-sm-12"><strong>Lounge</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Windows and mirrors to be cleaned</li>\r\n 	<li>All furniture to be wipe cleaned</li>\r\n 	<li>Light fittings to be cleaned</li>\r\n 	<li>TV stands and other equipment to be cleaned</li>\r\n 	<li>Hoover under the sofa and armchair</li>\r\n 	<li>Cobwebs removed from ceilings</li>\r\n 	<li>Skirting boards an