of all cleaning chores.\r\n\r\n<strong>Please have a look at our End of Tenancy Cleaning checklist:</strong>\r\n<div class="row"><aside class="col-sm-6"><strong>Kitchen</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>De-scale sink and taps and polish surfaces</li>\r\n 	<li>Wipe clean inside all cupboards and drawers</li>\r\n 	<li>Wash and clean all work surfaces</li>\r\n 	<li>Floors to be cleaned, vacuumed, and mopped</li>\r\n 	<li>All kitchen appliances including oven to be cleaned inside/out</li>\r\n 	<li>Wipe clean light fittings</li>\r\n 	<li>Wipe clean skirting boards</li>\r\n 	<li>Bins to be cleaned inside/out</li>\r\n 	<li>Clean the extractor fan</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</aside><aside class="col-sm-12"><strong>Bathroom</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>De-scale shower area</li>\r\n 	<li>Wipe clean tiles and fittings</li>\r\n 	<li>Wipe clean windows and mirrors</li>\r\n 	<li>De-scale and disinfect toilet inside/out</li>\r\n 	<li>Wipe clean ventilation extractor if accessible</li>\r\n 	<li>Floors vacuumed, washed and mopped</li>\r\n 	<li>Wipe clean skirting boards</li>\r\n 	<li>Any cupboards or fixtures to be cleaned</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</aside>\r\n<div class="clearfix hiddex-xs"></div>\r\n<aside class="col-sm-12"><strong>Bedrooms</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>All Furniture to be wipe cleaned inside/out</li>\r\n 	<li>All doors and hinges to be cleaned</li>\r\n 	<li>Windows and mirrors to be wiped leaving no smears</li>\r\n 	<li>Light fittings to be wipe cleaned</li>\r\n 	<li>Vacuum under bed and furniture</li>\r\n 	<li>Cobwebs cleaned from ceilings</li>\r\n 	<li>Floors vacuumed, and mopped where applicable</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</aside><aside class="col-sm-12"><strong>Lounge</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Windows and mirrors to be cleaned</li>\r\n 	<li>All furniture to be wipe cleaned</li>\r\n 	<li>Light fittings to be cleaned</li>\r\n 	<li>TV stands and other equipment to be cleaned</li>\r\n 	<li>Hoover under the sofa and armchair</li>\r\n 	<li>Cobwebs removed from ceilings</li>\r\n 	<li>Skirting boards and radiators wipe cleaned</li>\r\n 	<li>Doors to be cleaned</li>\r\n 	<li>Socket fittings wipe cleaned</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</aside>\r\n<div class="clearfix hidden-xs"></div>\r\n<aside class="col-sm-12"><strong>Hallway and Stairs</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Carpeted areas vacuumed</li>\r\n 	<li>Wood floors scrubbed and mopped</li>\r\n 	<li>Skirting boards and radiators wipe cleaned</li>\r\n 	<li>Light fittings cleaned</li>\r\n 	<li>Cobwebs removed from ceilings</li>\r\n 	<li>Windows and mirrors wipe cleaned</li>\r\n 	<li>Socket fittings wipe cleaned</li>\r\n 	<li>Staircase treads, handrails cleaned</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</aside></div>\r\nWe at Clean&amp;Clean provide high quality end of tenancy cleaning service covering the whole of London. We cover all London postcodes and some areas within the Greater London. We do have great cleaning packages to suit all needs. Discounts are available when you order two or more services together.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class="row"><aside class="col-sm-12">\r\n<div class="nxs-clear nxs-padding-top10"></div>\r\n<h4 class="nxs-title ">End of Tenancy Cleaning Prices and Move out cleaning prices</h4>\r\n<table id="table-l1461765042" class="table table-responsive table-striped table-hover">\r\n<thead class="">\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Property</th>\r\n<th>Flat</th>\r\n<th>House</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>Studio flat</td>\r\n<td>£85</td>\r\n<td>N/A</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>1 Bedroom</td>\r\n<td>£95</td>\r\n<td>N/A</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>2 Bedroom 1 bathroom</td>\r\n<td>£115</td>\r\n<td>£135</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>2 Bedroom 2 bathroom</td>\r\n<td>£125</td>\r\n<td>£135</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>3 Bedroom 1 bathroom</td>\r\n<td>£140</td>\r\n<td>£150</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>3 Bedroom 2 bathroom</td>\r\n<td>£150</td>\r\n<td>£160</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>4 Bedroom 1 bathroom</td>\r\n<td>£165</td>\r\n<td>£175</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>4 Bedroom 2 bathroom</td>\r\n<td>£175</td>\r\n<td>£180</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>4 Bedroom 3 bathroom</td>\r\n<td>£185</td>\r\n<td>£195</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>5 Bedrooms or more</td>\r\n<td>Call for a quote</td>\r\n<td>Call for a quote</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</aside><aside class="col-sm-6">\r\n<h4 class="nxs-title ">Carpet Cleaning</h4>\r\n<div class="nxs-clear nxs-padding-top10"></div>\r\n<table id="table-a4459754837" class="table table-responsive table-striped table-hover">\r\n<thead class="">\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Property Type</th>\r\n<th>Price</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>Single Bedroom</td>\r\n<td>£15</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>Double Bedroom</td>\r\n<td>£20</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>Lounge / Dining room</td>\r\n<td>£25</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>Hallway</td>\r\n<td>£15</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>Staircase (up to 15 steps)</td>\r\n<td>£15</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>Landing</td>\r\n<td>£5</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>Toilet / Bathroom</td>\r\n<td>£5</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>Rug (small)</td>\r\n<td>£10</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>Rug (medium)</td>\r\n<td>£15</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>Rug (large)</td>\r\n<td>£20</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</aside><aside class="col-sm-6">\r\n<h4 class="nxs-title ">Upholstery Cleaning</h4>\r\n<div class="nxs-clear nxs-padding-top10"></div>\r\n<table id="table-b4459754837" class="table table-responsive table-striped table-hover">\r\n<thead class="">\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Property Type</th>\r\n<th>Price</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>Armchair</td>\r\n<td>£15</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>2 Seater sofa</td>\r\n<td>£20</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>3 Seater sofa</td>\r\n<td>£30</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>4 Seater sofa</td>\r\n<td>£35</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>Dining chair</td>\r\n<td>£5</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>Landing</td>\r\n<td>£5</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>Curtains (half length)</td>\r\n<td>£20</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="">\r\n<td>Curtains (full length)</td>\r\n<td>£30</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</aside></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>Please note: Minimum call out charge of <strong>£40 </strong>applies for <strong>carpet, upholstery and curtains cleaning. </strong>If applicable congestion charge fee also applies. </em>\r\n\r\n<p class="number-list-heading"><strong><em>1) Do you supply cleaning materials and equipment? </em></strong></p>\r\n\r\nClean&amp;Clean supplies everything needed for the required cleaning service free of charge. We’ll not try to charge you any additional fees for cleaning materials and equipment.\r\n\r\n<p class="number-list-heading"><strong><em>2) Do you charge extra on weekends and bank holidays? </em></strong></p>\r\n\r\nClean&amp;Clean would not charge you extra for bookings on weekends and bank holidays. We work 7 days a week including bank holidays and the price always remains the same.\r\n\r\n<p class="number-list-heading"><em><strong>3) </strong><strong>Do you charge VAT or any other additional fees? </strong></em></p>\r\n\r\nClean&amp;Clean would not charge you VAT. Thus, the price you are quoted is the price you would pay for the service. No additional fees or hidden costs.\r\n\r\n<p class="number-list-heading"><strong><em>4) Is oven cleaning included? </em></strong></p>\r\n\r\nClean&amp;Clean will clean your oven inside and out as part of our End of tenancy Cleaning Service. Further, we’ll clean all other cleaning appliances free of charge.\r\n\r\n<p class="number-list-heading"><strong><em>5) Do you clean windows? </em></strong></p>\r\n\r\nInternal window cleaning is included, but we can also clean your windows externally as long as our cleaners can reach them for an additional charge.\r\n\r\n<p class="number-list-heading"><strong>6) Do you take a deposit?  </strong></p>\r\n\r\nFor smaller jobs, you don’t have to pay anything upfront. For some larger properties, 10% deposit may be required to be paid on the day.\r\n\r\n<p class="number-list-heading"><strong><em>7) Are you insured? </em></strong></p>\r\n\r\nWe have full public liability insurance up to £1,000,000 and employers liability insurance specifically designed for a cleaning services company.\r\n\r\n<p class="number-list-heading"><em><strong>8)</strong></em> <strong><em>Do you defrost the freezer?</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\nThe freezer has to be defrosted by the client to ensure that our cleaners can clean the unit inside and out.\r\n\r\n<p class="number-list-heading"><strong><em>9) </em></strong><strong><em>Do you work outside London?</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\nWe provide services to all London postcodes and some areas within M25 only.\r\n\r\n<p class="number-list-heading"><em><strong>10)</strong></em> <strong><em>Do you clean walls?</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\nWe don’t clean walls as when treated the paint can be damaged. Further, it is not an end of tenancy cleaning requirement.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>Our team is ready to provide you with a bespoke end of tenancy cleaning service so why don’t you give us a call today. We are looking forward to hear from you.</em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</section>', 'End of tenancy cleaning', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '27-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-26 00:18:01', '2017-04-26 00:18:01', '', 27, 'http://cleanandclean.24s.us/2017/04/26/27-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);

