(7, 2, '2017-04-11 11:40:15', '2017-04-11 11:40:15', '<section id="about-page">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="about-page-left-col col-sm-12"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/about-us-clean-clean.jpg" />\r\nWe started our company Clean&amp;Clean in 2006 with the simple aim of helping people to successfully hand over their rented properties. Since then, we have grown to become one of London''s best known cleaning companies offering complete end of tenancy cleaning services. Our mission is to constantly improve on customer service and provide unmatched support.\r\n\r\nSignificant amount of our work come from recommendations. Our company constantly receives commendations from our customers. We provide cleaning services to the leading estate agents in the capital and our company is well aware of the cleaning requirements for an end of tenancy cleaning service. Rest assured that you would hand over your property back in the desired condition in order to get your full deposit back.\r\n\r\n\r\nWe also invest significantly in improving our equipment and methods to keep up to date with the latest trends in the cleaning sector. Our cleaners undertake two weeks training before being able to work for our company. In addition our personnel is carefully vetted, fully insured, and professionally in-house trained. We do not employ subcontractors, and all cleaners work directly for the company.\r\n\r\n\r\nOur strong belief in our brand made us the company we are today. Clean&amp;Clean stands for quality, professionalism and excellent customer support. We put our heart and soul into what we do so we can provide you with hassle free experience. Our goal is to continue maintaining quality brand with string ethics.\r\n</div>\r\n</section>', 'About us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2017-04-21 14:50:47', '2017-04-21 14:50:47', '', 0, 'http://cleanandclean.24s.us/?page_id=7', 0, 'page', '', 0),
