(11, 2, '2017-04-11 11:40:33', '2017-04-11 11:40:33', '<section class="faq-page col-sm-12">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p class="bolder question">Do you supply cleaning materials and equipment?</p>\r\n<p>Clean&amp;Clean supplies everything needed for the required cleaning service free of charge. We’ll not try to charge you any additional fees for cleaning materials and equipment.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p class="bolder question">Do you charge extra on weekends and bank holidays?</p>\r\n<p>Clean&amp;Clean would not charge you extra for bookings on weekends and bank holidays. We work 7 days a week including bank holidays and the price always remains the same.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p class="bolder question">Do you charge VAT or any other additional fees?</p>\r\n<p>Clean&amp;Clean would not charge you VAT. Thus, the price you are quoted is the price you would pay for the service. No additional fees or hidden costs.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p class="bolder question">Is oven cleaning included?</p>\r\n<p>Clean&amp;Clean will clean your oven inside and out as part of our End of tenancy Cleaning Service. Further, we’ll clean all other cleaning appliances free of charge.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p class="bolder question">Do you clean windows?</p>\r\n<p>Internal window cleaning is included, but we can also clean your windows externally as long as our cleaners can reach them. Balcony windows will be cleaned from inside and outside.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p class="bolder question">Do you take a deposit?</p>\r\n<p>For smaller jobs, you don’t have to pay anything upfront. For some larger properties, 10% deposit is paid on the day of the booking.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p class="bolder question">Are you insured?</p>\r\n<p>We have full public liability insurance up to £1,000,000 and employers liability insurance specifically designed for a cleaning services company.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p class="bolder question">Where I can find your Privacy Policy or Terms and Conditions?</p>\r\n<p>You can find our privacy policy by clicking the link here: <a href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a> - Clean and Clean\r\nOr Terms and Conditions by clicking the link here: <a href="/terms-and-conditions/">Terms and Conditions</a> - Clean and Clean</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</section>', 'FAQ', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'faq', '', '', '2017-04-25 11:57:24', '2017-04-25 11:57:24', '', 0, 'http://cleanandclean.24s.us/?page_id=11', 0, 'page', '', 0),
