(104, 2, '2017-04-12 12:58:25', '2017-04-12 12:58:25', '<h1>About</h1>\r\nWe started our company Clean&amp;Clean in 2006 with the simple aim of helping people to successfully hand over their rented properties. Since then, we have grown to become one of London''s best known cleaning companies offering complete end of tenancy cleaning services. Our mission is to constantly improve on customer service and provide unmatched support.\r\n\r\nSignificant amount of our work come from recommendations. Our company constantly receives commendations from our customers. We provide cleaning services to the leading estate agents in the capital and our company is well aware of the cleaning requirements for an end of tenancy cleaning service. Rest assured that you would hand over your property back in the desired condition in order to get your full deposit back.\r\n\r\nWe also invest significantly in improving our equipment and methods to keep up to date with the latest trends in the cleaning sector. Our cleaners undertake two weeks training before being able to work for our company. In addition our personnel is carefully vetted, fully insured, and professionally in-house trained. We do not employ subcontractors, and all cleaners work directly for the company.\r\n\r\nOur strong belief in our brand made us the company we are today. Clean&amp;Clean stands for quality, professionalism and excellent customer support. We put our heart and soul into what we do so we can provide you with hassle free experience. Our goal is to continue maintaining quality brand with string ethics.', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '7-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-12 12:58:25', '2017-04-12 12:58:25', '', 7, 'http://cleanandclean.24s.us/2017/04/12/7-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(105, 2, '2017-04-12 12:58:45', '2017-04-12 12:58:45', '<h1>After builders cleaning</h1>\r\nHave you had builders working at your property? Have they left a mess behind them? Clean&amp;Clean can help you to clean your property leaving no dust behind. Our vast experience in conducting after builders cleaning can guarantee your full satisfaction. We won’t leave the premises until you are fully satisfied with our cleaning service.\r\n\r\nOur cleaning teams are fully equipped, insured, and vetted to ensure quality service and professionalism. We work 7 days a week including bank holidays at no additional charge. Our prices are fixed and unlike others we don’t do hidden charges. What you will be quoted is what you will be paying for the service.\r\n\r\nWe also have professional and up to date cleaning equipment that we successfully utilise in our cleanings. Let us help you get you property back into shape and dust free. Our cleaners undergo extensive in house training and all our personnel is working directly for the company.\r\n\r\n<strong>After Builders Cleaning benefits:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Removing of labels from bathrooms and kitchen appliances</li>\r\n 	<li>Dusting walls and ceilings</li>\r\n 	<li>Oven cleaning and all other kitchen appliances cleaned inside/out</li>\r\n 	<li>Vacuum and mop all floors throughout the property</li>\r\n 	<li>Cleaning materials and equipment included</li>\r\n 	<li>Satisfaction Guaranteed</li>\r\n 	<li>24/7 customer support</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIn addition to your after builders cleaning you can book carpet or upholstery cleaning service. By booking two or more services together we can provide you with great savings. Call our friendly team today to find out more, or simply visit this <a href="/prices">page</a> for pricing.', 'After builders cleaning', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '48-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-12 12:58:45', '2017-04-12 12:58:45', '', 48, 'http://cleanandclean.24s.us/2017/04/12/48-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(106, 2, '2017-04-12 12:59:09', '2017-04-12 12:59:09', '<h1>Carpet cleaning</h1>\r\nDo you need to clean your carpets professionally as part of your end of tenancy cleaning? Or you just want to steam clean them? Whatever your needs Clean&amp;Clean can help. Our carpet cleaning technicians are fully trained with NCCA (national carpet cleaners association) to ensure provision of quality service. In addition our carpet cleaners are fully insured and vetted.\r\n\r\nWe use the latest equipment from Prochem – the best known brand for provision of carpet cleaning materials and equipment. Our method for cleaning the carpets is by steam cleaning. Steam cleaning of carpets is known to be the most powerful and effective in cleaning the carpets. There are many benefits associated with having your carpets professionally cleaned. Not only your carpet will look clean and fresh, but also steam-cleaned carpets can improve air quality and eliminate dirt, stains and bacteria. Our powerful hot water extraction machine will reach the roots of your carpets and will clean and disinfect.\r\n\r\n<strong>Our Carpet Cleaning Process:</strong><strong> </strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Upon assessment of your carpet fibre, our carpet-cleaning technician will determine the best cleaning solution for your carpets.</li>\r\n 	<li>Pre-testing the cleaning solution to prevent any colour migration. We only use eco-friendly cleaning solutions that are save for your children and pets.</li>\r\n 	<li>We will carefully remove any furniture and vacuum the area with professional vacuum cleaner for best suction results</li>\r\n 	<li>Pre-spray treatment is the next step. The spray will ensure removal of oily material embedded in your carpet fibres.</li>\r\n 	<li>Next, we will apply stain removal chemicals to your carpet stains.</li>\r\n 	<li>In the sixth step, we will use the hot water extraction machine to deep clean the carpets.</li>\r\n 	<li>And finally we will apply Scotchguard to protect your carpets against dirt and tough stains.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nOur carpet cleaning prices are inclusive of all cleaning materials and equipment needed to carry out the job. We won’t charge you any additional fees such as parking fees. We cover the whole of London and some areas in Greater London. To see our competitive prices, please visit this <a href="/prices">page</a>.', 'Carpet cleaning', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '44-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-12 12:59:09', '2017-04-12 12:59:09', '', 44, 'http://cleanandclean.24s.us/2017/04/12/44-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(107, 2, '2017-04-12 12:59:49', '2017-04-12 12:59:49', '<h1>Contact</h1>\r\n<iframe style="border: 0;" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d5732.964514594174!2d-0.18036156140497867!3d51.58458967182908!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x48761a0e318be717%3A0xfefd6a1f0ad7e5b7!2sLyttelton+Rd%2C+London+N2+0DQ%2C+UK!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1491999235350" width="100%" height="250" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe>\r\n<div class="row"><aside class="col-sm-6"><strong>Customer Support is Available:</strong><em>Office Opening hours:</em>\r\nMon-Fri 09am – 7pm\r\nSaturday 10am – 6pm\r\nSunday 10am – 5pm\r\n\r\n<strong>Company Address:</strong> Office 47, 57 Lytteltonrd,\r\nHampstead Garden Suburb, London, N2 0DQ\r\n\r\n<strong>Tel:</strong> <a href="tel:02086140730">0208 6140 730</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:office@cleanandclean.london">office@cleanandclean.london</a>\r\n\r\nWe provide cleaning services to all of Central London and Greater London\r\n\r\n</aside><aside class="col-sm-6">[contact-form-7 id="26" title="Contact page"]</aside></div>', 'Contact', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-12 12:59:49', '2017-04-12 12:59:49', '', 17, 'http://cleanandclean.24s.us/2017/04/12/17-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(108, 2, '2017-04-12 13:00:46', '2017-04-12 13:00:46', '<h1>Deep cleaning</h1>\r\nYour tenants left your property a mess? The property hasn’t been cleaned for years? Don’t despair. Our professional cleaners specialising in deep cleaning will get back your property to its former glory. We have been conducting deep cleaning services for years and our experienced cleaners will resolve any cleaning problems. We are well equipped and knowledgeable when it comes down to providing perfect deep cleaning service.\r\n\r\nUnlike our competitors who use subcontractors, we provide in-house training and all our personnel is working directly for the company. Rest assured that our cleaners are fully insured, carefully vetted and professionally trained.\r\n\r\nOur Deep cleaning service is very comprehensive, and will clean your property from top to bottom. All kitchen appliances including the oven will be cleaned inside and out. Your satisfaction is guaranteed and we won’t leave the property until you are fully satisfied with the service. We won’t leave a single spot not cleaned, and will vacuum under beds and furniture.\r\n\r\n<strong>Deep cleaning benefits:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cleaning your property from top to bottom</li>\r\n 	<li>Cleaning of all kitchen appliances including the oven</li>\r\n 	<li>De-scaling of bathroom areas and kitchen sinks</li>\r\n 	<li>Provision of all cleaning materials</li>\r\n 	<li>Specialised and trained cleaning teams</li>\r\n 	<li>Fully insured cleaning service</li>\r\n 	<li>24/7 customer support</li>\r\n 	<li>Satisfaction Guaranteed</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDon’t forget that we have great saving packages when booking two or more services together. We constantly update our offers, so why don’t you give us a call to find out how much you can save today. Alternatively, you can visit this page for pricing and offers.', 'Deep cleaning', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '46-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-12 13:00:46', '2017-04-12 13:00:46', '', 46, 'htt