(214, 2, '2017-04-24 12:42:51', '2017-04-24 12:42:51', '<section class="move-cleaning col-sm-12">\r\n<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/end-of-tenancy-cleaning-london@2x.jpg" alt=""class="alignleft" />\r\n\r\nClean&amp;Clean is London’s best-known cleaning company for providing specialist move out cleaning services. Moving out of a property is stressful enough, and to deal with all those cleaning chores would add more strain. Save yourself the trouble of cleaning and hire professionals to do it for you. We offer top rated cleaning services at the most competitive rates in London. Our cleaners are insured, trained, and vetted for additional piece of mind.\r\n\r\nWe use the latest equipment and technology in conducting move in/out cleaning services. Our experienced cleaners can advise you on the best cleaning methods for your property to ensure quality and efficiency. We’ll also provide you with all cleaning materials and equipment; hence you don’t have to supply anything for the cleaning. We work 7 days a week including bank holidays with no extra charges.\r\n\r\nOur move in/out cleaning is very comprehensive, and we’ll clean your property from top to bottom. Oven cleaning is included internally and externally as well as all other kitchen appliances. Windows will be cleaned internally and externally where accessible.\r\n\r\n<strong>Move in/out cleaning benefits:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Satisfaction Guaranteed</li>\r\n 	<li>Cleaning materials and equipment included</li>\r\n 	<li>Oven clean included</li>\r\n 	<li>24/7 Customer support</li>\r\n 	<li>Rapid response often on the same day</li>\r\n 	<li>Insured cleaning service</li>\r\n 	<li>Professionally in-house trained cleaning teams</li>\r\n 	<li>Comprehensive cleaning service (top to bottom)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="italic">We do offer great package deals when you incorporate two or more services together. Our offers constantly change, so why don’t you call our friendly team to find out how much you can save. A