(226, 2, '2017-04-24 13:31:44', '2017-04-24 13:31:44', '<aside></aside>\r\n<div class="faq-wrapper"><aside><em>Do you supply cleaning materials and equipment?</em>\r\nClean&amp;Clean supplies everything needed for the required cleaning service free of charge. We’ll not try to charge you any additional fees for cleaning materials and equipment.</aside>&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<aside><em>Do you charge extra on weekends and bank holidays?</em>\r\nClean&amp;Clean would not charge you extra for bookings on weekends and bank holidays. We work 7 days a week including bank holidays and the price always remains the same.</aside>&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<aside><em>Do you charge VAT or any other additional fees?</em>\r\nClean&amp;Clean would not charge you VAT. Thus, the price you are quoted is the price you would pay for the service. No additional fees or hidden costs.</aside>&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<aside><em>Is oven cleaning included?</em>\r\nClean&amp;Clean will clean your oven inside and out as part of our End of tenancy Cleaning Service. Further, we’ll clean all other cleaning appliances free of charge.</aside>&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<aside><em>Do you clean windows?</em>\r\nInternal window cleaning is included, but we can also clean your windows externally as long as our cleaners can reach them. Balcony windows will be cleaned from inside and outside.</aside>&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<aside><em>Do you take a deposit?</em>\r\nFor smaller jobs, you don’t have to pay anything upfront. For some larger properties, 10% deposit is paid on the day of the booking.</aside><aside><em>Are you insured?</em>\r\nWe have full public liability insurance up to £1,000,000 and employers liability insurance specifically designed for a cleaning services company.</aside>&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<aside><em>Where I can find your Privacy Policy or Terms and Conditions?</em>\r\nYou can find our privacy policy by clicking the link here: Privacy Policy - Clean and Clean\r\nOr Terms and Conditions by clicking the link here: Terms and Conditions - Clean and Clean</