(253, 2, '2017-04-25 11:56:05', '2017-04-25 11:56:05', '<section class="deep-cleaning col-sm-12">\r\n<img src="/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/end-of-tenancy-cleaning-london@2x-1.jpg" alt=""class="alignleft" />\r\n\r\nYour tenants left your property a mess? The property hasn’t been cleaned for years? Don’t despair. Our professional cleaners specialising in deep cleaning will get back your property to its former glory. We have been conducting deep cleaning services for years and our experienced cleaners will resolve any cleaning problems. We are well equipped and knowledgeable when it comes down to providing perfect deep cleaning service.\r\n\r\nUnlike our competitors who use subcontractors, we provide in-house training and all our personnel is working directly for the company. Rest assured that our cleaners are fully insured, carefully vetted and professionally trained.\r\n\r\nOur Deep cleaning service is very comprehensive, and will clean your property from top to bottom. All kitchen appliances including the oven will be cleaned inside and out. Your satisfaction is guaranteed and we won’t leave the property until you are fully satisfied with the service. We won’t leave a single spot not cleaned, and will vacuum under beds and furniture.\r\n\r\n<strong>Deep cleaning benefits:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cleaning your property from top to bottom</li>\r\n 	<li>Cleaning of all kitchen appliances including the oven</li>\r\n 	<li>De-scaling of bathroom areas and kitchen sinks</li>\r\n 	<li>Provision of all cleaning materials</li>\r\n 	<li>Specialised and trained cleaning teams</li>\r\n 	<li>Fully insured cleaning service</li>\r\n 	<li>24/7 customer support</li>\r\n 	<li>Satisfaction Guaranteed</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class="italic">Don’t forget that we have great saving packages when booking two or more services together. We constantly update our offers, so why don’t you give us a call to find out how much you can save today. Alternatively, you can visit this <a href="/prices/">pa